HELP XT_SET_VALUES                                  Steve Knight, Oct 93
                                                    SIREN Project
xt_set_values( WIDGET, BINDING1, ..., BINDINGn )

A convenience function that substitutes for (and is more efficient than)
the following

    XtSetValues(
        WIDGET,
        XptArgList( [ BINDING1 ... BINDINGn ] )
    )
